  "texts": [
    "Both linear and kernel SVMs were tested, with the RBF kernel applied for non-linear classification and regularization parameter C = 0.80 for linear SVM.",
    "We explored several deep learning models, including CNN, BiLSTM, BiLSTM+Attention, Keras+CNN, GloVe+CNN, and GloVe+BiLSTM.",
    "The CNN model utilized 128 filters with a kernel size of 5 and 24 neurons in the dense layer.",
    "In the BiLSTM+Attention model, ReLU was used in the dense layer and Sigmoid in the output layer.",
    "BiLSTM (Schuster and Paliwal, 1997) enhanced performance by capturing bidirectional contextual information."
